---
// Static, self-contained 404 page (no BaseLayout / no `t` dependency).
// Astro emits dist/404.html, which Cloudflare Pages serves for unknown URLs —
// this replaces the previous behaviour where any missing path returned 200
// with the root redirect page. Trilingual (ES / EN / CA), dark theme, noindex.
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es" class="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0A0A0A" />
    <title>404 — RestoreLab</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --dark: #0A0A0A;
        --navy: #0D1B2A;
        --blue: #1B3A5C;
        --accent: #2A7FFF;
        --gold: #D4A537;
        --white: #FFFFFF;
        --light: #F5F5F5;
        --muted: #9BA7B4;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #0D1B2A 55%, #1B3A5C 100%);
        color: var(--light);
        font-family: 'DM Sans Variable', 'DM Sans', system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      .wrap { max-width: 40rem; width: 100%; }
      .code {
        font-size: clamp(5rem, 22vw, 10rem);
        line-height: 0.9;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--gold));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
      }
      .titles { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
      .titles .t {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--white);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      }
      .titles .t.primary { font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 5vw, 1.9rem); }
      .titles .t.secondary { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; margin-top: 0.35rem; }
      .lead { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; margin: 0.75rem auto 2rem; max-width: 32rem; }
      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
        border-radius: 0.6rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        transition: transform 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      }
      .btn:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 3px; }
      .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
      .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
      .btn-primary:hover { background: #1f6fe6; }
      .btn-ghost {
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--light);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      }
      .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
      .langs {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1.25rem;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .langs a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
      .langs a:hover { color: var(--white); text-decoration: underline; }
      .langs a:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 3px; border-radius: 0.25rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <p class="code">404</p>
      <div class="titles">
        <h1 class="t primary">Página no encontrada</h1>
        <p class="t secondary">Page not found · Pàgina no trobada</p>
      </div>
      <p class="lead">
        La página que buscas no existe o se ha movido. ·
        The page you’re looking for doesn’t exist. ·
        La pàgina que busques no existeix.
      </p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/es">Ir al inicio</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/es/services">Ver servicios</a>
      </div>

      <nav class="langs" aria-label="Idioma / Language / Idioma">
        <a href="/es" hreflang="es">Español</a>
        <a href="/en" hreflang="en">English</a>
        <a href="/ca" hreflang="ca">Català</a>
      </nav>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
